snippet: A duplex penthouse with four terraces perched in one of the majestic twin towers of the Eldorado co-op on Central Park West is poised to enter the market.
abstract: Duplex penthouse with four terraces at the Eldorado, Art Deco landmark at 300 Central Park West, is poised to enter market for $29 million.
lead_paragraph: A duplex penthouse with four terraces perched in one of the majestic twin towers of the Eldorado co-op on Central Park West is poised to enter the market.

headline.seo: $29 Million at the Eldorado on Central Park West
